OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FAfter Scotland's First Minister Humza
OL,7,FYousaf announced he's stepping down,
OL,8,Fthe SNP must hold its second
OL,9,Fleadership contest in barely a year
OL,11,Fhas announced his resignation as first
OL,12,Fminister of Scotland after a year in
OL,13,Foffice.
OL,15,FOn Monday, the SNP leader confirmed he
OL,16,Fwould step down from his post
OL,17,Ffollowing the breakdown of a power-
OL,18,Fsharing deal with the Scottish Greens
OL,19,Fand launch of two separate no
OL,20,Fconfidence motions.
