OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FWhile Mr Yousaf said he will remain in
OL,7,Fpower until a suitable replacement can
OL,8,Fbe found, an SNP leadership contest
OL,9,Fhas begun giving the party 28 days to
OL,10,Felect a new first minister.
OL,12,FNo member has yet put forward their
OL,13,Fbid for leadership but there are
OL,14,Fcontenders who are expected to run for
OL,15,Fthe job.
OL,17,FHere, breaks down the runners expected
OL,18,Fto throw their names forward.
OL,20,FKate Forbes
