OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FThe Skye, Lochaber and Badenoch MSP is
OL,7,Fperhaps the most likely replacement
OL,8,Fafter she narrowly lost to Mr Yousaf
OL,9,Fin the fiery leadership contest to
OL,10,Freplace Nicola Sturgeon just over a
OL,11,Fyear ago.
OL,13,FAnd as finance secretary under Ms
OL,14,FSturgeon, Ms Forbes has been known to
OL,15,Fhelp her government through tough
OL,16,Fcrises, stepping into the role and
OL,17,Fdelivering a budget at short notice
OL,18,Fafter her predecessor, Derek Mackay,
OL,19,Fresigned in disgrace in 2020.
