OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FA Free Church of Scotland member, Ms
OL,7,FForbes' first run at the leadership
OL,8,Fwas not smooth sailing as her stance
OL,9,Fon social issues is at odds with many
OL,10,Fwithin her own party, particularly her
OL,11,Fopposition to gender reform.
OL,13,FA key obstacle in her leadership,
OL,14,Fhowever, would be the Scottish Greens,
OL,15,Fthey have previously ruled out working
OL,16,Fwith her over her views so it is
OL,17,Funlikely she would command the support
OL,18,Fto effectively rule.
