OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FIn the last leadership contest, Ms
OL,7,FForbes did not have the backing of
OL,8,Fmost of her own SNP MSPs but did win
OL,9,Fover a significant number of members,
OL,10,Flosing the closely-fought leadership
OL,11,Felection by 47.9% of the vote compared
OL,12,Fto Mr Yousaf's 52.1%.
OL,14,FJohn Swinney
OL,16,FThe loyal deputy first minister to Ms
OL,17,FSturgeon could throw his hat in the
OL,18,Fring as an SNP MSP with significant
OL,19,Fexperience.
