OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FSpeaking to broadcasters following Mr
OL,7,FYousaf's announcement, he confirmed he
OL,8,Fwould give the prospect of running for
OL,9,Fleader "very careful consideration"
OL,10,Fover the coming days.
OL,12,F"I've been somewhat overwhelmed by the
OL,13,Frequests that have made me to me from
OL,14,Fcolleagues across the party.
OL,16,F"I'm giving that issue very active
OL,17,Fconsideration and it's likely I will
OL,18,Fhave more to say about that in the
OL,19,Fdays to come," he added.
