OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FHe has been an MSP since the Scottish
OL,7,FParliament's inception in 1999,
OL,8,Fserving North Tayside, and previously
OL,9,Frepresenting the same constituency at
OL,10,FWestminster in 1997.
OL,12,FMr Swinney led his party in Holyrood
OL,13,Fbetween 2000 and 2004 during the SNP's
OL,14,Ftime on the opposition benches.
OL,16,FHe has held a raft of cabinet
OL,17,Fpositions, including education and
OL,18,Ffinance and resigned at the same time
OL,19,Fas Ms Sturgeon.
