OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FHe ruled himself out of the 2023
OL,7,Fleadership race, stating he had to put
OL,8,Fhis young family first. However, the
OL,9,FSNP politician could take the reins to
OL,10,Funite his party in a time of turmoil.
OL,12,FMairi McAllan
OL,14,FThe Clydesdale MSP has been tipped as
OL,15,Fa future leader as she quickly moved
OL,16,Fup the ranks despite only being
OL,17,Felected in 2021.
