OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FAt the age of 31, Ms McAllan would
OL,7,Fbecome the youngest first minister,
OL,8,Fbut her portfolio in Holyrood shows
OL,9,Fshe is already capable of handling a
OL,10,Fsignificant brief.
OL,12,FThe party's rising star was given a
OL,13,Fministerial post for environment,
OL,14,Fbiodiversity and land reform in May
OL,15,F2021, shortly after being elected.
OL,17,FBut, under Mr Yousaf, she quickly
OL,18,Fascended to a cabinet post just two
OL,19,Fyears later, taking on the Transport,
OL,20,FNet Zero and Just Transition portfolio.
