OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FHer brief was widened further in
OL,7,FFebruary 2024 after Neil Gray was
OL,8,Fmoved to health secretary. She became
OL,9,Fwellbeing economy, net zero and energy
OL,10,Fsecretary.
OL,12,FMs McAllan announced she was expecting
OL,13,Fher first child in February 2024,
OL,14,Fadding she planned to take maternity
OL,15,Fleave in the summer with a scheduled
OL,16,Freturn for March 2025.
OL,18,FThe wealth of experience held by Neil
OL,19,FGray could make him a likely contender
OL,20,Ffor leadership.
