OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FHe is thought to be the closest ally
OL,7,Fof Mr Yousaf but may be able to unite
OL,8,Fparliament.
OL,10,FHe is a former MP and became an MSP in
OL,11,F2021 serving as a culture and
OL,12,Finternational development minister
OL,13,Fbefore being promoted to economy, fair
OL,14,Fwork and energy secretary around a
OL,15,Fyear later.
OL,17,FHe stepped up to become health
OL,18,Fsecretary following the resignation of
OL,19,FMichael Matheson.
