OL,3,CWho could succeed Humza Yousaf as
OL,4,CScotland's first minister?
OL,6,FFormer teacher Jenny Gilruth
OL,7,Frepresents Mid Fife and Glenrothes and
OL,8,Fis the current education secretary.
OL,10,FHer brief is one of the toughest as
OL,11,Fshe faces pressure to address the
OL,12,Fincreasing issue of violence in
OL,13,Fschools.
OL,15,FShe has also held transport minister
OL,16,Fbriefs and Europe, migration and
OL,17,Finternational development minister.
